description: Non-material amendments to planning permission (Ref: 2015/04076/VAR) granted 10 July 2017; amendments sought relate to Phase 2 of the development and involve; variation of condition 3 (replacement drawings) which identify changes including; the repositioning of the break in the building line and introduction of further balconies on the eastern side of the Central Avenue; vehicular access and landscape changes; provision of three glazed links between blocks fronting the River Thames walkway; partial increase in the depth of part of the basement level and the building heights of Blocks D, E and the Central Avenue; amendments to windows and other external details; reduction in car parking spaces; change in residential unit/habitable rooms mix and provision of communal spaces.
